data.description: The seller is now offering $5,000 towards the buyer's closing costs!! Welcome home to this charming brick haven in the coveted Bell Fork neighborhood! With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this cozy abode is ready to become your personal sanctuary. Step inside and prepare to be amazed! This beauty underwent a stunning remodel a few years back, leaving no stone unturned. The cool, modern gray paint palette effortlessly complements the sleek laminate flooring and upgraded fixtures, creating an ambiance that screams ''home sweet home''. One of the highlights of this gem is the living room, featuring elegant French doors that open up to an additional living area.  Talk about versatility! This space is perfect for setting up a spacious office or even a cozy den to unwind and relax in after a long day. The kitchen is an absolute dream come true for any aspiring chef! Equipped with stainless steel appliances, pristine white cabinets, and a trendy subway tile backsplash, this culinary sanctuary will make your cooking adventures pure bliss. Prepare to whip up delicious meals with ease and style! Let's not forget the peaceful retreat that awaits you in the primary bedroom. The ensuite bathroom, complete with a trendy barn door, adds a touch of contemporary chic to your oasis. Plus, two more generously sized bedrooms make sure there's plenty of space for your loved ones or guests. And guess what? There's even a storage shed in the back, providing the perfect spot for stashing away all your outdoor essentials. Don't miss out on the chance to call this lovely home yours! Schedule a viewing today and let your homeownership dreams become a reality. Act fast, because this beauty won't stay on the market for long!
